cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.SD 

This paper is about creating a dataset and task formulation for dialogue systems to improve their ability for sophisticated common grounding. This involves natural language processing, artificial intelligence, and machine learning, which are all covered by the Computer Science sub-categories of cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.LG. Additionally, the paper discusses the importance of human communication and the need for evaluation and analysis of complex models, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.HC (human-computer interaction) and cs.SD (social and information networks).
